conbody.p:
Unless otherwise prohibited, when excluding task or delivery orders from business or contract clearance, Contracting officers typically document their clearance exclusion decision, the record of which should be included in the contract file for every order.  Contracting officers may utilize the Fair Opportunity Order Clearance Exclusion MFR template (not yet uploaded to 
						PGI Library
					) to exclude an order from business or contract clearance.
